TestNG
-------------
TestNG -  Test New Generation is Java based automation framework

Advantages:
-------------
1) Manage test cases & test suites
2) We can also group test cases
3) Prioritize
4) Parameterization
5) Parallel testing - Cross browser testing
6) Reports

Steps:
----
1) Install TestNG library within eclipse
2) Add TestNG Library to java project.

Supported versions:
-------------------
Java Version: 1.8.x
Eclipse Version: 2020-12 (4.18) & Lower versions supporting TestNG
TestNG Version: 7.2.0 latest (or lower)

*** Note: Follow the document to Install TestNG in Eclipse...


TestSuite--> TestCases -- Test Steps
Package --> Class ---> TestMethods

